ash → sendTransaction → confirmTransaction → refreshBalance\n   430→  - **`joinTierRound`**: Fetches tier rounds, creates new round via `buildCreateRoundTx` if none exists, or joins via `buildJoinRoundTx`. Stores `activeRoundMeta` (tierIndex + roundNumber) for subsequent tx building\n   431→  - **`buyMoreEntriesAction`**: Builds tx via `buildBuyMoreEntriesTx`, sends, refreshes round\n   432→  - **`startSpin`**: New action — builds tx via `buildStartSpinTx`, sends, transitions to \"spinning\" phase\n   433→  - **`claimPayout`**: Builds tx via `buildClaimPayoutTx`, sends, auto-transitions back to lobby\n   434→  - **`handleAutoClaim`**: Auto-triggered when polling detects VRF fulfilled and player is winner\n   435→  - **Polling**: 5s interval when in active round (polls `fetchRound`), 15s for lobby (`fetchAllTierRounds`)\n   436→  - **Error handling**: `parseTransactionError()` helper maps wallet/program errors to user-friendly messages\n   437→  - **New context fields**: `spinning`, `startSpin`, `error`, `clearError` (additive — no breaking changes to existing consumers)\n   438→- Exported `getLordProgram` from chain.ts (was previously private)\n   439→- Added `fetchRoundNumberForTier()` helper to derive round number from on-chain config\n   440→\n   441→**Verification**: `pnpm typecheck` — 17/17 packages pass. `pnpm lint` — 17/17 packages pass (0 errors, 43 pre-existing warnings).\n   442→\n   443→**Status**: Done\n   444→\n   445→## Iteration 15 — 2026-02-26T23:25:28Z — OK\n   446→- **Log**: iteration-015.log\n   447→\n   448→## Iteration 16 — Update tier types to use SOL amounts\n   449→\n   450→**Item**: Phase D, item 3 — Update tier types to use SOL amounts\n   451→\n   452→**What was done**:\n   453→- Updated `types.ts`:\n   454→  - Changed `entryAmount` comment from `// Cost per entry in $` to `// Cost per entry in SOL`\n   455→  - Changed `poolAmount` comment from `// Total $ in pool` to `// Total SOL in pool`\n   456→- Updated `TierLobby.tsx`:\n   457→  - Ch